00:37:15.936 --> 00:37:18.676 A:middle
We want to build a healthy web

00:37:19.786 --> 00:37:20.606 A:middle
for everyone.

00:37:20.896 --> 00:37:22.286 A:middle
And intelligent tracking

00:37:22.286 --> 00:37:24.586 A:middle
